# SQL Injection

![](http://imgs.xkcd.com/comics/exploits_of_a_mom.png)

## Resources

[OWASP.org - SQL Injection](https://www.owasp.org/index.php/SQL_Injection) - The OWASP Foundation's entry on SQL Injection attacks.

[PHP Manual - SQL Injection](http://www.php.net/manual/en/security.database.sql-injection.php) - PHP Manual entry on SQL Injection. Contains some code examples to make it pretty clear why this is a bad idea.
